---
layout: base
title: Home
---
<section class="hero">
  <h1>Kia ora! I'm Sam from New Zealand</h1>
  <p class="lead">Welcome to my personal website where I share thoughts, experiences, and stories from Aotearoa New Zealand.</p>
</section>

<section class="subscription">
  <h2>Stay Updated</h2>
  <p>Subscribe to receive the latest updates straight to your inbox.</p>
  
  <form id="subscription-form" class="email-form">
    <div class="form-group">
      <label for="email">Email Address</label>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your@email.com">
    </div>
    <button type="submit" class="button">Subscribe</button>
  </form>
  <p class="small">I respect your privacy and won't spam your inbox.</p>
</section>

<section class="recent-posts">
  <h2>Recent Posts</h2>
  
  {% set posts = collections.post | reverse %}
  {% set recentPosts = posts.slice(0, 3) %}
  
  <div class="post-grid">
    {% for post in recentPosts %}
    <article class="post-card">
      <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <time datetime="{{ post.date.toISOString() }}">{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</time>
      {% if post.data.description %}
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      {% endif %}
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read More â†’</a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  
  <p class="view-all"><a href="/blog/">View all posts</a></p>
</section>
